        <item>
          <actionDesc>Reported to House without amendment, Part I</actionDesc>
          <text><![CDATA[<p>(This measure has not been amended since it was introduced. The summary has been expanded because action occurred on the measure.)</p> <p><b>Endangered Species Litigation Reasonableness Act </b></p> <p>(Sec. 2) This bill amends the Endangered Species Act of 1973 to replace the current standard for awarding court costs, including attorney fees, in citizen suits with the federal judicial code standard for awarding costs to a prevailing party. </p>]]></text>
